Special to The New York Times
GREENWICH, Conn., Feb. 16.--John H. Tyson is married again. Mrs. Tyson No. 4, who was Miss Olive Hawley and later Mrs. Alexander H. Bass, said tonight that she and Mr. Tyson were married on Feb. 5. The ceremony was performed by Justice of the Peac...
